<br>
<font size="3"><font color="#D03A40"><b>VRCHAT KMART EXECUTIVE COMMITTEE:</b></font></font> <br> <br>
<font size="3"><font color="#41A3A9"><b>Ericirno</font></b><br>
</b>Map Creator, Store Manager, President and Chief Executive Officer
<p>
<font size="3"><font color="#41A3A9"><b>Null</font></b><br>
Assistant Manager.
<p>
<br><br>
<font size="3"><font color="#D03A40"><b>VRCHAT KMART HUMAN RESOURCES:</font><br><br></b>
<font size="3"><font color="#41A3A9"><b>Howl</font></b><br>
Occasionally a smartass, often gets angry at Division.
<p>
<font size="3"><font color="#41A3A9"><b>Headpatmesenpai</font></b><br>
Definitely not a loli, don't mess with his computer in the Personnel office.
<p>
<br><br>
<font size="3"><font color="#D03A40"><b>VRCHAT KMART MANAGEMENT:</font><br><br></b>
<font size="3"><font color="#41A3A9"><b>LittleFoot</font></b><br>
5% Wholesome. Co-Manages Security and Loss Prevention department.
<p>
<font size="3"><font color="#41A3A9"><b>BlazeTox1c</font></b><br>Owns an Ericirno body pillow. Co-Manages Security and Loss Prevention department.
<p>
<font size="3"><font color="#41A3A9"><b>Burezu</font></b><br>
LPD Officer and hasn't paid his bill. Co-Manages the Apparel department
<p>
<font size="3"><font color="#41A3A9"><b>Labracadabrador</font></b><br>
Leader of the <font color="#41A3A9"><a href=https://discord.gg/EKrnXj4>The L.A.B. Unit PMC</a></font></font> Co-Manages the Apparel department.
<p>
<font size="3"><font color="#41A3A9"><b>Hat Kid</font></b><br>
Lead protagonist in the game <i>A Hat in Time</font></i>. Manages Front End operations.
<p>
<font size="3"><font color="#41A3A9"><b>ET Blast</font></b><br>
Kind of a dweeb, but that's okay. Manages the Electronics and Entertainment departments.
<p>
<font size="3"><font color="#41A3A9"><b>Zemlin</font></b><br>
Likes guns. Manages the Sporting Goods department.
<p>
<font size="3"><font color="#41A3A9"><b>Cramso</font></b><br>
Really enjoys giving tours. Manages Public Relations and store tours.
<p>
<br><br>
<font size="3"><font color="#D03A40"><b>VRCHAT KMART MARKETING:</font><br><br></b>
<font size="3"><font color="#41A3A9"><b>ace_verco</font></b><br>
Good with photography, even in virtual reality.
<p>
